# Bubble Field

entities.YetAnotherHelper/BubbleField.placements.name.normal=Bubble Column

entities.YetAnotherHelper/BubbleField.attributes.description.strength=The strength with which the bubbles push objects (If value is 0 or negative this won't work).
entities.YetAnotherHelper/BubbleField.attributes.description.direction=The direction the bubbles move.
entities.YetAnotherHelper/BubbleField.attributes.description.activationMode=Determines on which condition the bubble column activates.
entities.YetAnotherHelper/BubbleField.attributes.description.flag=The session flag this bubble column reacts to (when Activation Mode is "only if flag [in]active").
entities.YetAnotherHelper/BubbleField.attributes.description.liftOffOfGround=Whether or not the bubble column should push the player away from ground. This includes lifting them off of the floor (if they are standing on one), and pushing them away from walls that they are next to.

# Flag Kill Barrier

entities.YetAnotherHelper/FlagKillBarrier.placements.name.normal=Flag Kill Barrier

entities.YetAnotherHelper/FlagKillBarrier.attributes.description.flag=The flag needed for the barrier to be active.
entities.YetAnotherHelper/FlagKillBarrier.attributes.description.trueColorHex=Color of the barrier when it is active.
entities.YetAnotherHelper/FlagKillBarrier.attributes.description.falseColorHex=Color of the barrier when it is inactive.

# Spiked Jump Through Controller

entities.YetAnotherHelper/SpikeJumpThruController.placements.name.normal=Spike Jump Thru Controller

